n trust fsb is a privately owned investment manager the firm also provides fiduciary banking fiduciary real estate trust estate administration and financial planning services to its clients it primarily provides its services to individuals and high net worth individuals the firm also caters to pension and profit sharing plans charitable organizations corporations and state or municipal government entities it manages separate client focused equity and fixed income portfolios the firm invests in the public equity and fixed income markets across the globe it invests in small medium and largecap companies to make its equity investments the firm also invests in real first american trust fsb is a privately owned investment manager the firm also provides fiduciary banking fiduciary real estate trust estate administration and financial planning services to its clients it primarily provides its services to individuals and high net worth individuals the firm also caters to pension and profit sharing plans charitable organizations corporations and state or municipal government entities it manages separate client focused equity and fixed income portfolios the firm invests in the public equity and fixed income markets across the globe it invests in small medium and largecap companies to make its equity investments the firm also invests in real estate the firm employs a fundamental analysis with a combination of topdown and bottomup stock picking approach to make its investments it was founded in  and is based in santa ana california with additional offices in newport beach california san diego california san diego california san diego california phoenix arizona las vegas nevada and san bernardino california first american trust fsb operates as a subsidiary of first american financial corporation detailed description  first american waysanta ana ca united statesfounded in  phone  fax  wwwfirstamtrustcom key executives for first american trust fsb mr thomas martin kelley chief exe